{
  "id": "adv_bond_aoi_01_02",
  "title": "井川葵2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "愛、せっかくのオフなのに\n本当に付き合ってもらって良かったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ it's a rare day off\nIs it really okay for you to spend time with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　私、前からお菓子作りに興味あったんです！\nラーメンは得意ですけど、それ以外はあまり経験なくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I've always been interested in making sweets!\nRamen is my specialty‚ but I don't have much experience with anything else",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "クッキーは焼くだけだから、そんなに難しくないよ\n愛ならすぐに僕より美味しいのを作れると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just baking cookies‚ it's not that difficult\nI think Ai can quickly make something more delicious than me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "初心者にプレッシャーをかけないで下さいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ don't pressure beginners~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだし、沢山焼いてみんなに配ろう\n寮のみんなにも日頃世話になってるしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the first time‚ let's bake a lot and share it with everyone\nWe're always owed to everyone in the dorm",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7333369227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、{user}さんにもですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ to {user}-san‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君にもか……\nそうだ、いいことを思いついた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To {user}-kun‚ too…\nYeah‚ I had a good idea",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだから\nあげる人に合った形のクッキーにしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preferably‚\nmake cookies in a shape that suits the giver",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どういうことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "食べる人のイメージに合った動物にするのさ\nこころなら、小悪魔とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make it an animal that matches the image of person eating it\nIf it's Kokoro‚ it's a little devil",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "小悪魔は動物なんでしょうか……？\nあと、形が複雑過ぎる気が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are little devils animals…?\nAlso‚ I think shape is too complicated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7333320617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央は……なんだと思う？\n動物に例えるなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio is… what do you think?\nCompare her to an animal",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　莉央さんは……強いから……\nライオン……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Rio-san is… strong…\nLion…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕はもっと強いと思うな。シベリアトラくらいだよ\nいや、人食いシベリアトラかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's stronger than that. Like a Siberian tiger\nNo‚ it's a man-eater Siberian tiger",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんの指定は細か過ぎて\n作れる気がしないんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san's instructions are so detailed\nthat I don't think I can make it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、僕が人食いシベリアトラを作るから\n愛は小悪魔を頼むよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'll make a man-eater Siberian tiger\nAi‚ make a little devil",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと葵さん\n小悪魔ってどう作ればいいか分かりませんよ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait a second‚ Aoi-san\nI don't know how to make a little devil~!!",
        "id": ""
